              <TBODY>
              <TR bgColor=3D#eeeeee>
                <TD width=3D"100%">What does it take to establish =
web-based=20
                  document management? <BR><BR>Thursday's WebDAV =
tutorial=20
                  examined readily-available fixtures for simple =
introduction of=20
                  web-based document management on the standard office =
desktop.=20
                  <BR><BR>What else is needed to qualify and establish =
managed=20
                  web-document practices? <BR><BR>This workshop explores =
the gap=20
                  between components of generic technology and what it =
takes to=20
                  operate smoothly with managed documents in practical =
office=20
                  settings. <BR><BR>We're after a road map for pulling =
together=20
                  available information, identifying what else is =
needed, and=20
                  exploring ways of obtaining it through community =
effort. Our=20
                  target is a practical guide to successful, affordable=20
                  practices. </TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE><!-- Comment =
invitation message -->
